      • processChoice

        private static boolean processChoice​(char ch,
                                     java.util.Scanner kybd)
        Executes the users menu choice

        Sets the indicator if a game will be played to true, play, takes in the users menu choice and runs it into a switch. Runs the appropriate case then returns play.

        Parameters:
        ch - User's menu choice
        kybd - Scanner object
        Returns:
        play True if game will be played, false otherwise

      • whoGoesFirst

        private static boolean whoGoesFirst​(Game game,
                                    Roll theDice)
        Determines which player goes first

        Rolls the dice twice and stores each value. Checks for which roll is greater, returns boolean value based on result.

        Parameters:
        game - The game being played
        Returns:
        boolean True player 1 goes first, false player 2 goes first
